milestones.description: Vani Morea has become the top scorer for PNG in ODIs with 280 runs, going past Lega Siaka's 245
Norman Vanua has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for PNG, going past Pokana's 1
This is the lowest match aggregate (399) involving teams P.N.G. & U.A.E. in ODIs
U.A.E.'s 103-run win against P.N.G. is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 82-run win against P.N.G.
Ghulam Shabber has broken the record for most dismissals (12) in ODIs for UAE, going past Swapnil Patil's 11
Naveed has broken the record for most sixes (12) in ODIs for UAE, going past Shaiman Anwar's 12
Mahuru Dai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for PNG, going past Vani Morea
